<section class="py-10 px-4 w-full animate-on-scroll fade-up relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-10">
            <h2 class="font-fact text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white mb-4 title-glow">
                Tu Camino al Éxito
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-xl mx-auto text-sm">Metodología ágil en 3 pasos.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative pl-4 md:pl-0">
            <div class="absolute left-[29px] md:left-1/2 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/10 via-primary/50 to-primary/10 md:-translate-x-1/2"></div>

            <div class="space-y-8 md:space-y-12 relative z-10">
                
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0 group relative">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right pl-16 md:pl-0 order-1">
                        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">1. Auditoría & Diseño</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs md:text-sm">Analizamos tu marca y diseñamos una propuesta visual única en Figma.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute left-[20px] md:left-1/2 top-0 md:top-1/2 w-5 h-5 bg-[#050505] border-2 border-primary rounded-full md:-translate-x-1/2 md:-translate-y-1/2 z-20 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-1/2 order-2"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0 group relative">
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-1/2 order-1"></div>
                    <div class="absolute left-[20px] md:left-1/2 top-0 md:top-1/2 w-5 h-5 bg-[#050505] border-2 border-primary rounded-full md:-translate-x-1/2 md:-translate-y-1/2 z-20 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pl-12 pl-16 order-2">
                        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">2. Desarrollo Astro</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs md:text-sm">Programamos tu web línea a línea. Sin plantillas pesadas, pura velocidad.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-4 md:gap-0 group relative">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:pr-12 md:text-right pl-16 md:pl-0 order-1">
                        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">3. Despegue</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs md:text-sm">Pruebas finales, optimización SEO y publicación en servidor global.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute left-[20px] md:left-1/2 top-0 md:top-1/2 w-5 h-5 bg-[#050505] border-2 border-primary rounded-full md:-translate-x-1/2 md:-translate-y-1/2 z-20 group-hover:scale-125 group-hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_0_10px_#FF6363]"></div>
                    <div class="hidden md:block w-1/2 order-2"></div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
